1931;;Stolen Heaven;;American;;George Abbott;;Nancy Carroll, Phillips Holmes, Louis Calhern;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stolen_Heaven;;Mary, a girl of the streets, and Joe, a young thief, rob twenty thousand dollars and decide to spend all the money and then commit suicide. But Joe's conscience speaks louder and he confesses the crime. He goes to prison knowing that Mary will wait for him.